{"tid":1745741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳海底撈撈出疑似護墊異物","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:23:37.000Z","uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"978e4323a3dca0ff89eb21f08887f97185f84c08","tid":1745741,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/22/Tojvla.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F22%2FTojvla.png&h=5085dbe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名女子光顧深圳海底撈卓越店期間，在火鍋湯底撈出異物，初時以為是肉，細看後懷疑是衛生護墊，覺得噁心，要求店舖賠償人民幣100萬元。店方稱根據生產流程，所有環節不會出現此異物，並已交警方處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2170000/2171288/Ux1tUHyf_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2170000%2F2171288%2FUx1tUHyf_1024.jpg&h=af5b3753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合內地媒體報導，9月28日，一名姓倪的女子報稱在深圳海底撈卓越店吃火鍋，吃了幾口，在鍋中撈出疑似衛生護墊的異物。她稱：「剛開始我以為是肉，一看不對，後面以為是紙巾，但看清楚了也不對。」她找經理詢問，經理稱這是廚房用來墊肉的紙，並取出一包墊肉紙對照，還說可帶她參觀後堂、工廠，堅稱火鍋食材絕無問題。姓倪女子指油鍋裡的東西與拿來對比的墊肉紙並不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n理論期間，女子要求海底撈退還前一日光顧店舖支付的款項，然後要求賠償人民幣100萬，之後改為50萬，又毀壞店內一些餐具。海底撈職員報警，女子曾提出上告法庭，並指即使對方關店、賠償800萬也無法解決。<br />\n<br />\n分店負責人對記者表示，已向顧客退還前一天800元的用膳費用。不過，經店方查看閉路電視，發現事件存有疑點。9月28日當天，女子獨自入店內用餐，選好座位後向店員表示不用服務，全程自行處理。用膳約半小時後，向店員報稱發現異物。店員當時表示，根據生產流程，所有環節均不會出現此異物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2170000/2171288/nNSMIgfV_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2170000%2F2171288%2FnNSMIgfV_1024.jpg&h=df45e861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重慶印象火鍋深圳梅林店經理看到報導後，與海底撈聯絡，表示姓倪女子於9月29日光顧時同樣報稱發現有疑似「衛生巾」的異物，同樣要求索償。警方調查後發現，該名女子有躁鬱症，具體情況仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2171288/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E6%92%88%E6%92%88%E5%87%BA%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E8%AD%B7%E5%A2%8A%E7%95%B0%E7%89%A9%E3%80%80%E9%A1%A7%E5%AE%A2%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%98%AF%E8%82%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2171288%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595%25E6%2592%2588%25E6%2592%2588%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A2%258A%25E7%2595%25B0%25E7%2589%25A9%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E8%2582%2589%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%2584%259F%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyllKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=73d78d63\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2171288/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E6%92%88%E6%92%88%E5%87%BA%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E8%AD%B7%E5%A2%8A%E7%95%B0%E7%89%A9%E3%80%80%E9%A1%A7%E5%AE%A2%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%98%AF%E8%82%89%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC</a>"},{"pid":"b6388257df693fd116ad5e86ec4e614824a55d96","tid":1745741,"uid":34075,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:16:22.000Z","msg":"popo 話食海底撈 係咪即係想食m巾"},{"pid":"f1cc42798297123fbac7b33c7cb13e9b2bb1efe5","tid":1745741,"uid":66365,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"點睇都似自己放落去啦，當人傻既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331ca356f2b3645e3efa1fda3b2c45e410783ccf","tid":1745741,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"一條友食左800蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c6ba90b5b99bbbfb7309d03c2cc66a3cfa1c07","tid":1745741,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"食生命麵包好過"},{"pid":"9afbadd6372cb82df40c0fe3c9603b06a271d5c3","tid":1745741,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"好合理啫 曱甴係喺d垃圾堆度躝架啦"},{"pid":"55534cb9ac842dd95f2ab7709836a72a9f814ad4","tid":1745741,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"碰瓷"}]}